### Register user and inspect password hash in database
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hashuser1",
  "email": "hashuser1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Register another user with same password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hashuser2",
  "email": "hashuser2@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

